reviewText: This was a awesome video for me in regards to learning Pre-Algebra it seems it was straight to the point on how to carry out the operations. I rented it as a DVD from the Library a workbook comes with it but I did not receive that from the Library. I wish amazon.com carried it on DVD but it does not seem they do.

If you buy this tape your life will be easy.  This Tape will teach
you algebra in a simple way.  No more excuse to fail algebra.
